==Headslapper==

===Etymology===
'''Headslapper''' is a slang term with several common meanings.&nbsp; The derivation of the first meaning below is fairly self-evident, as is the second, which clearly follows from it.&nbsp; The third usage appears to have originated in the Bitmines group on [[w:Internet CB Network|ICB]], the [[w:Internet CB Network|Internet CB Network]].&nbsp; In this usage, the term may have been originated by the Reverend J. B. Bell.&nbsp; In the admittedly sometimes-odd context of Bitmines, it's about equal parts derogatory and compliment, and is canonically explained (in the Bitmines context) approximately as follows:

<blockquote>'You're out somewhere, and you see this ravishingly, stunningly gorgeous [person of the desired sex], and you think to yourself, "Gad, I'd give my left [insert body part here] to date him/her."&nbsp; Then thirty seconds later, you slap yourself upside the head and say, "What was I '''thinking'''?!?" when you remember that he/she is barking mad.'</blockquote>

===Noun===
''(headslapper)''  (''plural:'' ''(headslappers)'')
# Any mistake of such obvious stupidity that you slap yourself in disbelief that you just committed it
# The exact moment when you realize you have made such a mistake; also, ''(headslapper moment)''
# A person you consider extremely physically desirable, but far too unstable to risk involvement with

